tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE marketing_campaigns (
  campaign_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  campaign_name VARCHAR(255),
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE,
  conversion_rate DECIMAL(5,2)
);

CREATE TABLE campaign (id INT PRIMARY KEY,
name VARCHAR,
start_date DATE,
end_date DATE);

CREATE TABLE conversion_rate (id INT PRIMARY KEY,
campaign_id INT,
conversion_rate FLOAT,
conversion_date DATE);

CREATE TABLE conversion_rates ( campaign_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  campaign_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  conversion_rate FLOAT NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE campaigns ( campaign_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  campaign_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  start_date DATE NOT NULL,
  end_date DATE NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE visitors ( visitor_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  campaign_id UUID NOT NULL,
  visit_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
)
